gw.plugin.billing

Interface BillingPaymentInstrument


  • public interface BillingPaymentInstrument
    The BillingPaymentInstrument class provides:
    • The PublicID as a String
    • The PaymentMethod as a AccountPaymentMethod
    • The DisplayName as a String
    • The OneTime as a Boolean
    • The Token as a String
    • The detail field as (@link java.lang.String)
